18#include "ODRowReader.h"

22#include <cmath>

27namespace ZXing {
28namespace OneD {
29
30Result
31RowReader::decodeSingleRow(int rowNumber, const BitArray& row) const
32{
33 std::unique_ptr<DecodingState> state;
34 return decodeRow(rowNumber, row, state);
35}
36
37Result RowReader::decodePattern(int, const PatternView&, std::unique_ptr<RowReader::DecodingState>&) const
38{
39#ifdef ZX_USE_NEW_ROW_READERS
40 return Result(DecodeStatus::_internal);
41#else
42 return Result(DecodeStatus::NotFound);
43#endif
44}
